[[Image:crotchlift.jpg|thumb|350px|Collegiate wrestlers utilize "Crotchlift"]]
==English==
===Etymology===
From French ''[[croc]]'', "hook".
===Noun===
'''crotch'''
# the [[area]] where something [[fork]]s or [[branches]], a [[ramification]] takes place
#:''There is a child sitting in a crotch of that tree.''
# the ([[ventral]]) area of a person's body where the [[leg]]s fork from the [[trunk]]
#:''He was kicked in his crotch.''
====Translations====
*French: [[fourche]] ''f'' (1)
*German: [[Gabelung]] ''f'' (1), [[Schritt]] ''m'' (2)
*Swedish: (gren)[[klyka]] {{c}} (1), [[skrev]] {{n}} (2), [[gren]] {{c}} (2)